48 A report so approved shall be signed by the chairperson of the committee and filed with
49 the Clerk of the House of Representatives.
50 (D) In the absence of an approved report, the chairperson may file with the Clerk of the
51 House of Representatives a copy of the minutes of the meetings of the committee in lieu
52 thereof.
53 (7) Abolishment. The committee shall stand abolished on December 1, 2025.
